Uses of Package
teachersV3

Packages that use teachersV3
teachersV3 This package contains all classes for manipulation. 
teachersV3.core This package contains all the manipulation for files. 
teachersV3.io This package contains all implementation for the reading. 
teachersV3.jFreeChart This package contains the chart. 
 

Classes in teachersV3 used by teachersV3
Evaluation
          Contains all the evaluation for the corrected student, the grader (professor) and the mark.
Professor
          The professor can put marks to students depending of the promotion, the id of the student and if he wants to add/modify a mark.
Promotion
          The Promotion permits to sort students in promotions to know where they belong to.
Student
          A student is represented with an id, a promotion if he got one and can have marks (10 the maximum).
